description.en:
Baby Rabbit is the leading decentralized token on the BSC networks, using the innovative ‘Mall + App’ model!

Test applications and redeem rewards during the warm-up period for deployment to the official BSC network. The combination of network and offline, and the connection with the earlier operating Internet e-commerce platform - Amazon created the first online mall in the primary market!
